{
  "stem": "27770.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Every minute, this guy was beaten up, this one.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We shouldn't even have time to think.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After being there a week time, they felt that the people-- there will be something done.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They say we have to give him something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Can you imagine a guilt feeling?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they took out a big, big bath tub.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was putting under the bath tub four or six legs made for the bath tub outside, made fire under the bath tub, threw in beads or those green whatever it is-- cheap stuff-- and they made a soup the public should have a little warm soup.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So finally everybody was hoping, after a week time, being hungry, children were crying, screaming.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So suddenly, the soup was ready, a little hot water, and people started to stay in the line with a little dish to go and get the soup.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The first Jew, of course, most of them they didn't have beard.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They cut them off the beard already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "A father didn't recognize the son, and the son didn't recognize the father, and the wife didn't recognize the husband, because all their life they saw him with a beard, here without a beard.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he's staying there, one Jew, he still had a beard and staying with his little dish what has a holder.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they want to give him the first cup of soup.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was happy to bring it to his grandchild or even to his own baby.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the guy, this Hungarian officer, takes away from him the dish before he gets it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he says you see this holder?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Underneath there is dirt.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Dirt.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And if there is dirt, he didn't eat from his dish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The Jew would eat from the-- he beat him up so for this little dirt.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
